data.description: Seller ordered appraisal that came in at $700,000 in August 2023. Charming country estate nestled among 1.37 acres in Astoria! Features 4 beds/3 baths, wood flooring, picture windows, open concept floor plan with natural light. Great entry leads to inviting living room with a built-in surround sound system & pellet stove. Fully furnished kitchen includes brand-new dishwasher, stainless steel appliances, and osmosis water system. Convenient laundry room includes washer and dryer. Primary suite on main, separated for privacy. Water heater & efficient Cadet heaters. New electrical panel and wiring. Extensive, higher fenced backyard is dog proof, includes covered patio, patio, deck, firepit, wood shed, outbuilding. New roof and 9000-watt solar system owned, both installed in 2022. Fiber optics internet available. Recently surveyed and recorded property lines. Just a short drive from downtown Astoria, this property offers a perfect blend of tranquility and accessibility. Ideal for a vacation getaway or year-round living. Don't miss this opportunity to own your slice of paradise!
